          "result": {
            "type": "megamod:dialogue",
            "text": "Exactly! A School will educate the young ones and when they grow up, they will start with higher base skills than untrained adults. It is an investment in the future of our colony. Craft the hut block, place it, and let your builder handle the rest!",
            "options": [
              {
